{"tid":1591312,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得針對共產黨 好過針對中國？","createTime":"2019-09-24T05:57:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T06:08:50.000Z","uid":82006,"like":50,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"6c93a6ad2bfcd124732b2c1d5441223104a913ad","tid":1591312,"uid":82006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:57:34.000Z","msg":"因為小弟工作關係，大部分接觸既都係年老一輩同埋蝗國人，有時討論，佢地多數都係大中華膠，但一講到點睇黨，個個都（<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），大部分都話中國其實無問題，但係個黨出d政策同埋行動令到蝗國市民根本唔知咩事，當中資訊封鎖，強推政策都令到好多蝗國人不滿。<br />\n如果我地文宣做 愛國不等於愛黨會唔會connect 到？<br />\n紅底新聞就一味播燒國旗，侮辱國家etc...我地侮辱黨又點睇？"},{"pid":"2e1da9d463590e2a981c8dd4fefca8c20a84fb7b","tid":1591312,"uid":82006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T06:01:15.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"ff53009b6fe9f5a55549312c25797796daec0152","tid":1591312,"uid":82006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T06:02:36.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"5cf86b8ca0284c61864c65140810a493d7efa64b","tid":1591312,"uid":178440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T06:04:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e5bbca9233dccf2b1b8326d8865d49f9c0c670e","tid":1591312,"uid":282777,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T06:04:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c951f62d593ddcf6bff01e454995a7f57f9c8555","tid":1591312,"uid":282777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T06:05:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b1acdb813f314daa776130097cea0ad6c187b568","tid":1591312,"uid":282777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T06:05:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"46f0bc40d1984e41b2bbce51289e93324d244175","tid":1591312,"uid":140793,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T06:20:52.000Z","msg":"其實係 最好拉攏埋班反共分子 內部分化中國同中共"},{"pid":"baa3674cfaa39f91a9b671953ee706b63afdeebc","tid":1591312,"uid":82006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T